      Subinterfaces of TargetList.Projection in org.postgresql.pljava.model 
      Modifier and Type Interface Description
      interface  TupleDescriptor
      Conceptually, a TupleDescriptor is a list of Attribute, with a RegType that identifies its corresponding row type.
      static interface  TupleDescriptor.Ephemeral
      A descriptor that has been constructed on the fly and has not been interned.
      static interface  TupleDescriptor.Interned
      A descriptor that either describes a known composite type in the catalogs or has been interned in PostgreSQL's type cache, and has a distinct rowType that can be used to identify it.
